data.description: Country Come to Town.....  Beautiful 8.2 acres Blue Cutt Road. Very private  Gorgeous  architectural design home, 3 bedroom and 3.5 baths home with stone fireplace in the great room. Hardwood floors thru out. Tile in the bathrooms, jetted tub and separate shower in master. Downstairs fully finished basement with bathroom.  Storage galore. 20 x 25Work Shop/ Garage.  2 HVAC systems. The home was built energy efficient rock wool insulation even in the walls.  The home even comes with its own dirt track with jumps. Above ground pool with deck. Green house. Fenced backyard. Huge 8x40 storage container in backyard.
